Once created, messages are sent using function linphone_chat_room_send_message() . linphone_chat_room_send_message(chat_room,"Helloworld");/*sendingmessage*/

Incoming message are received from call back LinphoneCoreVTable.text_received voidtext_received(LinphoneCore*lc,LinphoneChatRoom*room,constLinphoneAddress*from,constchar*message){
printf("Message[%s]receivedfrom[%s]\n",message,linphone_address_as_string(from));
}

